cu.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an invalid enum 'invalid' will cause ASN.1 verbosity configuration errors and prevent proper message parsing.

du.explanation_en: Setting physCellId to a negative value -1 will cause physical cell ID validation errors and prevent cell configuration.
du.explanation_zh: 將 physCellId 設定為負值 -1 會導致物理細胞 ID 驗證錯誤，並阻止細胞配置。
